OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778817909
OL,3,CStudent dies in Reading meningitis
OL,4,Coutbreak as contacts offered
OL,5,Cantibiotics
OL,7,FClose contacts of people linked to a
OL,8,Fmeningitis outbreak in Reading, in
OL,9,Fwhich a student died, are being
OL,10,Foffered antibiotics as a precaution.
OL,12,FTwo other young people are being
OL,13,Ftreated after at least one case was
OL,14,Fconfirmed as meningitis B (MenB),
OL,15,Fwhich was linked to a cluster of fatal
OL,16,Fcases in Kent earlier this year.
OL,18,FIt is understood that the most recent
OL,19,Fcase in Berkshire is not the same
OL,20,Fstrain of MenB linked to the outbreaks
OL,21,Fin Kent in March.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
