OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778817909
OL,3,CStudent dies in Reading meningitis
OL,4,Coutbreak as contacts offered
OL,5,Cantibiotics
OL,7,FThe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,8,Fsaid risk to the public currently
OL,9,Fremains low.
OL,11,FIn a statement issued on Thursday, the
OL,12,FUKHSA said that its specialists were
OL,13,F"working with local authority and NHS
OL,14,Fpartners following three cases of
OL,15,Fmeningococcal infection (meningitis)
OL,16,Fin young people in Reading".
OL,26,@uD@AOUxD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
