OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778817909
OL,3,CStudent dies in Reading meningitis
OL,4,Coutbreak as contacts offered
OL,5,Cantibiotics
OL,7,F"Dear patients. We have been in
OL,8,Fcontact with the UK Health Security
OL,9,FAgency this morning (14th May)
OL,10,Fregarding the very sad news that a
OL,11,Fstudent at Henley College has died
OL,12,Fwith suspected meningococcal disease,"
OL,13,Fthe Hart Surgery said in a statement
OL,14,Fon Thursday evening.
OL,16,F"They have confirmed that they are
OL,17,Factively contacting those who may be
OL,18,Fat risk due to a close association
OL,19,Fwith the student involved.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@fO]xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778817909
OL,3,CStudent dies in Reading meningitis
OL,4,Coutbreak as contacts offered
OL,5,Cantibiotics
OL,7,F"If you have not been contacted by the
OL,8,FUK Health Security Agency, then
OL,9,Fcurrently you do not require any
OL,10,Ftreatment. Staff and students have
OL,11,Fbeen advised they can attend the
OL,12,Fcollege as usual.
OL,14,F"The number of confirmed cases is very
OL,15,Flow so there are currently no plans
OL,16,Ffor a local emergency meningitis
OL,17,Fvaccination programme."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUyD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
